---
// tools.astro — 工具 & 產品頁
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="工具 & 產品" description="玄學日報、交易指標、幣安監控、BitMart Card — 每一個都是實際在用的工具。">

  <!-- ============================================================
       Opening
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="tools-opening" data-reveal="slow">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="tools-title">工具決定你能看見什麼。</h1>
      <p class="tools-subtitle">
        這裡的每一個工具<br />
        都是我自己在用的東西<br />
        沒有例外。
      </p>
      <span class="amber-rule" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;"></span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       Tool 1 — 玄學日報 (odd: image right, text left)
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="tool-section tool-odd">
    <div class="container tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-text" data-reveal="left">
      <span class="section-number">01</span>
      <h2 class="tool-name">玄學日報</h2>
      <p class="tool-desc">
        八字 × 紫微斗數 × 人類圖<br />
        每日市場能量分析，一日一次。
      </p>
      <p class="tool-desc">
        不是預測，是框架<br />
        讓你知道今天適不適合進場、能量偏多還是偏空。
      </p>
      <p class="tool-price">15U <span>/ 月</span></p>
      <a href="#subscribe" class="arrow-link">找秋爸訂閱 →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-image" data-reveal="right">
      <img src="/images/xuanxue-daily.svg" alt="玄學日報 Telegram 預覽" class="tool-img tool-img--svg" />
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       Tool 2 — 交易指標 (even: image left, text right)
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="tool-section tool-even">
    <div class="container tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-image" data-reveal="left">
      <img src="/images/indicator.png" alt="交易指標 TradingView 截圖" class="tool-img" />
    </div>

    <div class="tool-text" data-reveal="right">
      <span class="section-number">02</span>
      <h2 class="tool-name">交易指標</h2>
      <p class="tool-desc">
        TradingView 上的聚合指標<br />
        整合七種技術分析，一個畫面讀懂進出場時機。
      </p>
      <p class="tool-desc">
        適合短單、中線、波段——<br />
        不是只能用在一種打法上。
      </p>
      <p class="tool-price">
        入群前兩個月免費使用<br />
        <span class="tool-price-alt">單獨訂閱 100U / 3 個月</span>
      </p>
      <a href="#subscribe" class="arrow-link">訂閱指標 →</a>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       Tool 3 — 幣安主流幣監控 (odd)
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="tool-section tool-odd">
    <div class="container tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-text" data-reveal="left">
      <span class="section-number">03</span>
      <h2 class="tool-name">Binance x Bitget 監控</h2>
      <p class="tool-desc">
        AI 聚合分析，每日早晚兩次<br />
        主流幣動態整理成文字，直接讀，不用自己盯盤。
      </p>
      <p class="tool-price tool-price--included">含在入群方案內</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-image" data-reveal="right">
      <img src="/images/binance-monitor.svg" alt="Binance x Bitget 監控 Telegram 預覽" class="tool-img tool-img--svg" />
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       返傭說明 — Confrontation section
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="rebate-section">
    <div class="container">
    <div class="rebate-grid">
      <div class="rebate-inner" data-reveal="left">
        <h2 class="rebate-title">關於返傭。</h2>

        <p class="rebate-warning">如果你覺得我在洗你的交易量——</p>

        <div class="rebate-body">
          <p>你用我的邀請碼，我拿返傭，是真的<br />
          我自己靠這個打法賺的，比返傭多很多，也是真的。</p>

          <p>那我們可能從一開始就不適合。</p>

          <p>
            如果你在兩個月後覺得這間交易所不適合你<br />
            沒關係，指標可以單獨訂閱，換回你習慣的地方繼續用。
          </p>

          <p>退路一直在，要不要走是你的選擇。</p>
        </div>

        <p class="rebate-english">The option is always there.</p>

        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;">
          <a href="https://www.bitmart.com/zh-TW/invite/cMPDb9" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="arrow-link" style="display: inline-flex;">
            → BitMart 邀請碼註冊
          </a>
          <a href="https://promote.mexc.com/a/pM06womH" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="arrow-link" style="display: inline-flex;">
            → MEXC 邀請碼註冊
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rebate-image" data-reveal="right">
        <img src="/images/rebate-bg.png" alt="" class="rebate-img" />
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       Tool 4 — BitMart Card (even)
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="tool-section tool-even tool-bitmart">
    <div class="container tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-image" data-reveal="right">
      <img src="/images/bitmart-card.png" alt="BitMart Card" class="tool-img tool-img--card" />
    </div>

    <div class="tool-text" data-reveal="left">
      <span class="section-number">04</span>
      <h2 class="tool-name">BitMart Card</h2>
      <p class="tool-desc">
        出金一直是加密貨幣的痛點<br />
        這張卡換個方式解決這件事——<br />
        直接在台灣日常消費裡用掉它。
      </p>
      <p class="tool-desc">
        綁定 Google Pay 和 Line Pay<br />
        手機感應，結帳。
      </p>

      <div class="cashback-table">
        <div class="cashback-row">
          <span class="cashback-label">超商 / 速食（7-11、全家、麥當勞）</span>
          <span class="cashback-rate">5% – 5.5%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cashback-row">
          <span class="cashback-label">外送 / 網購（FoodPanda、蝦皮）</span>
          <span class="cashback-rate">3.5% – 4%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cashback-row">
          <span class="cashback-label">一般消費</span>
          <span class="cashback-rate">3.5%</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="cashback-meta">
        免申請費。免年費。虛擬卡直接開<br />
        <em>VIP 等級靠合約交易量升級。高頻短單的交易量，本來就比一般人高。</em>
      </p>

      <p class="cashback-close">打單賺錢，刷卡也在賺。</p>
      <p class="cashback-english">That's the compounding effect of a consistent method.</p>

      <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;">
        <a href="https://my-fanpage.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="arrow-link" style="display: inline-flex;">
          → 了解 BitMart Card
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.bitmart.com/zh-TW/invite/cMPDb9" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="arrow-link" style="display: inline-flex;">
          → 邀請碼註冊
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       Tool 5 — MEXC × ether.fi Card (odd)
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="tool-section tool-odd tool-mexc-card">
    <div class="container tool-grid">
    <div class="tool-text" data-reveal="left">
      <span class="section-number">05</span>
      <h2 class="tool-name">MEXC × ether.fi 聯名信用卡</h2>
      <p class="tool-desc">
        專為高頻玩家打造的返現神卡<br />
        與 ether.fi 合作推出的高階 Visa 虛擬信用卡<br />
        福利結構非常直接，完全瞄準行動支付習慣。
      </p>

      <p class="tool-desc">
        Apple Pay / Google Pay 無縫綁定<br />
        申請過件後直接綁進手機錢包<br />
        全球能刷卡的終端機都能用加密資產結帳。
      </p>

      <div class="cashback-table">
        <div class="cashback-row">
          <span class="cashback-label">日常消費（咖啡、吃飯、搭車）</span>
          <span class="cashback-rate">3%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cashback-row">
          <span class="cashback-label">旅遊消費（機票、飯店預訂）</span>
          <span class="cashback-rate">5%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cashback-row">
          <span class="cashback-label">海外刷卡手續費</span>
          <span class="cashback-rate">0%</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="cashback-meta">
        免除國際交易手續費——<br />
        常買國外網購、訂閱 Netflix / Spotify 的人<br />
        <em>省下的 1.5% 海外手續費，長期算下來很可觀。</em>
      </p>

      <p class="cashback-close">打單賺錢，刷卡也在賺。兩張卡，兩種場景。</p>
      <p class="cashback-english">Two cards. Two ecosystems. One method.</p>

      <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;">
        <a href="https://www.mexc.com/zh-TW/learn/article/how-to-apply-for-the-mexc-%C3%97-ether-fi-credit-card/1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="arrow-link" style="display: inline-flex;">
          → 了解 MEXC × ether.fi Card
        </a>
        <a href="https://promote.mexc.com/a/pM06womH" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="arrow-link" style="display: inline-flex;">
          → 邀請碼註冊
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-image" data-reveal="right">
      <img src="/images/mexc-card.png" alt="MEXC × ether.fi Visa Card" class="tool-img tool-img--card" />
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       Section — 手續費試算器
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="calc-section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-number">06</span>
      <h2 class="calc-main-title">手續費試算器</h2>
      <p class="calc-main-desc">開倉前先算清楚成本，這是紀律的一部分。</p>

      <div class="calc-grid">

        <!-- BitMart 試算器 -->
        <div class="calc-card" id="calcBitmart">
          <h3 class="calc-title">BitMart 合約試算</h3>
          <div class="calc-form">
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label>計算模式</label>
              <select data-calc="mode">
                <option value="margin">USDT 本金 + 槓桿</option>
                <option value="quantity">幣種數量 (顆數)</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label>交易幣種</label>
              <select data-calc="coin">
                <option value="60000">BTC ($60,000)</option>
                <option value="3000">ETH ($3,000)</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label>訂單類型</label>
              <select data-calc="order">
                <option value="0.0006">Taker 吃單 (0.06%)</option>
                <option value="0.0002">Maker 掛單 (0.02%)</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label data-calc="amountLabel">投入本金 (USDT)</label>
              <input type="number" data-calc="amount" value="100" min="0" step="any" />
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field" data-calc="leverageWrap">
              <label>槓桿倍數 (最高 200x)</label>
              <div class="calc-slider-row">
                <input type="range" data-calc="leverage" min="1" max="200" value="100" />
                <span class="calc-lever-val" data-calc="leverageVal">100x</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="calc-results">
            <div class="calc-result-row">
              <span>總倉位價值</span>
              <span data-calc="totalValue">0.00 USDT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-result-row">
              <span>單邊手續費</span>
              <span class="calc-fee" data-calc="oneWay">0.00 USDT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-result-row">
              <span>一進一出成本</span>
              <span class="calc-fee" data-calc="roundTrip">0.00 USDT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-result-row calc-result-row--last" data-calc="percentWrap">
              <span>佔本金比例</span>
              <span class="calc-fee" data-calc="percent">0.00%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="calc-note">* Maker 0.02% / Taker 0.06%</p>
          <a href="https://www.bitmart.com/zh-TW/invite/cMPDb9" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="calc-cta">註冊 BitMart →</a>
        </div>

        <!-- MEXC 試算器 -->
        <div class="calc-card" id="calcMexc">
          <h3 class="calc-title">MEXC 極速合約試算</h3>
          <div class="calc-form">
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label>計算模式</label>
              <select data-calc="mode">
                <option value="margin">USDT 本金 + 槓桿</option>
                <option value="quantity">幣種數量 (顆數)</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label>交易幣種</label>
              <select data-calc="coin">
                <option value="60000">BTC ($60,000)</option>
                <option value="3000">ETH ($3,000)</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label>訂單類型 (統一費率)</label>
              <select data-calc="order">
                <option value="0.0004">Taker 吃單 (0.04%)</option>
                <option value="0.0004">Maker 掛單 (0.04%)</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label data-calc="amountLabel">投入本金 (USDT)</label>
              <input type="number" data-calc="amount" value="100" min="0" step="any" />
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field" data-calc="leverageWrap">
              <label>槓桿倍數 (最高 500x)</label>
              <div class="calc-slider-row">
                <input type="range" data-calc="leverage" min="1" max="500" value="100" />
                <span class="calc-lever-val" data-calc="leverageVal">100x</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="calc-results">
            <div class="calc-result-row">
              <span>總倉位價值</span>
              <span data-calc="totalValue">0.00 USDT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-result-row">
              <span>單邊手續費</span>
              <span class="calc-fee" data-calc="oneWay">0.00 USDT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-result-row">
              <span>一進一出成本</span>
              <span class="calc-fee" data-calc="roundTrip">0.00 USDT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-result-row calc-result-row--last" data-calc="percentWrap">
              <span>佔本金比例</span>
              <span class="calc-fee" data-calc="percent">0.00%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="calc-note">* 統一費率 Maker / Taker 皆 0.04%，市價逃命無額外成本。</p>
          <a href="https://promote.mexc.com/a/pM06womH" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="calc-cta">註冊 MEXC →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script is:inline>
    document.querySelectorAll('.calc-card').forEach(function(card) {
      var q = function(sel) { return card.querySelector('[data-calc="' + sel + '"]'); };
      var mode = q('mode'), coin = q('coin'), order = q('order');
      var amount = q('amount'), amountLabel = q('amountLabel');
      var leverageWrap = q('leverageWrap'), leverage = q('leverage'), leverageVal = q('leverageVal');
      var totalValue = q('totalValue'), oneWay = q('oneWay'), roundTrip = q('roundTrip');
      var percentWrap = q('percentWrap'), percent = q('percent');

      function fmt(n) {
        return n.toLocaleString('en-US', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 });
      }

      function calc() {
        var m = mode.value;
        var price = parseFloat(coin.value);
        var rate = parseFloat(order.value);
        var amt = parseFloat(amount.value) || 0;
        var lev = parseFloat(leverage.value);
        var total = m === 'margin' ? amt * lev : amt * price;
        var oneFee = total * rate;
        var twoFee = oneFee * 2;

        totalValue.textContent = fmt(total) + ' USDT';
        oneWay.textContent = fmt(oneFee) + ' USDT';
        roundTrip.textContent = fmt(twoFee) + ' USDT';

        if (m === 'margin' && amt > 0) {
          percent.textContent = ((twoFee / amt) * 100).toFixed(2) + '%';
        }
      }

      leverage.addEventListener('input', function() {
        leverageVal.textContent = leverage.value + 'x';
        calc();
      });

      mode.addEventListener('change', function() {
        if (mode.value === 'margin') {
          leverageWrap.style.display = '';
          amountLabel.textContent = '投入本金 (USDT)';
          amount.value = 100;
          percentWrap.style.display = '';
        } else {
          leverageWrap.style.display = 'none';
          amountLabel.textContent = '交易數量 (顆數)';
          amount.value = 1;
          percentWrap.style.display = 'none';
        }
        calc();
      });

      [coin, order, amount].forEach(function(el) {
        el.addEventListener('input', calc);
      });

      calc();
    });
  </script>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ---- Opening ---- */
  .tools-opening {
    padding: 160px 0 100px;
  }

  .tools-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    max-width: 14ch;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .tools-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  /* ---- Tool Sections ---- */
  .tool-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .tool-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 8vw;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .tool-odd .tool-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 45% 55%;
  }

  .tool-even .tool-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 55% 45%;
  }

  /* ---- Tool Images ---- */
  .tool-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 137, 26, 0.12);
  }

  .tool-img--svg {
    border: none;
    max-width: 420px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .tool-img--card {
    background: #F8F8F8;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: none;
  }

  /* ---- Tool Text ---- */
  .tool-name {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tool-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tool-price {
    color: var(--amber);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .tool-price span,
  .tool-price-alt {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    display: block;
  }

  .tool-price--included {
    color: var(--text-muted) !important;
    font-size: 0.95rem !important;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ---- 返傭 ---- */
  .rebate-section {
    padding: 120px 0;
  }

  .rebate-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6vw;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .rebate-inner {
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .rebate-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .rebate-warning {
    color: var(--red);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .rebate-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.4rem;
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .rebate-body p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .rebate-english {
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--amber);
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .rebate-image {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .rebate-img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 480px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  /* ---- BitMart ---- */
  .cashback-table {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .cashback-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 1rem 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .cashback-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .cashback-rate {
    color: var(--amber);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

